'''Klev''' was an assistant of [[Squarn]]'s who worked in [[Squarn's Junkyard]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Muugrah]].

==Biography==
When a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] arrived to get parts to repair the [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] of their ship, the ''[[Transorb]]'', they were met by Klev who led them to a permanently emplaced military surplus shelter module which served as the junk seller's office. Once there, he introduced them to Squarn.

